WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.000
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:44.000
[Episode 38]

01:55.229 --> 01:58.979
[Meeting Room]

02:01.290 --> 02:02.830
[Mr. Wei]

03:01.750 --> 03:02.630
This recording

03:02.630 --> 03:04.310
isn't directly related

03:04.310 --> 03:06.150
to the wiretapping incident,

03:06.630 --> 03:08.190
but we can use it

03:10.630 --> 03:11.590
against them.

03:12.250 --> 03:13.110
Exactly.

03:13.530 --> 03:15.530
Let's fan the flames for Wei Siyuan.

03:21.590 --> 03:22.320
Enjoy your meal.

03:22.320 --> 03:23.030
Thank you.

03:23.360 --> 03:24.590
The environment here is nice, right?

03:24.590 --> 03:25.150
Yes.

03:28.750 --> 03:29.560
Mrs. Wei.

03:32.070 --> 03:33.530
Hello. Please take a seat.

03:37.010 --> 03:38.230
So you are Xu Miyu.

03:39.850 --> 03:41.250
What do you want from me?

03:45.110 --> 03:46.570
Please take a look at this.

03:50.920 --> 03:51.680
Who is this?

03:51.940 --> 03:53.540
This is Lu Zhenzhen's child.

04:04.650 --> 04:06.230
[The DNA test]

04:06.260 --> 04:07.900
[on the parental relationship
between Nie Quan and Wei Siyuan]

04:11.530 --> 04:12.720
Why are you telling me this?

04:12.720 --> 04:14.650
Lu Zhenzhen's husband is my ex.

04:15.810 --> 04:17.670
They are now divorced.

04:18.029 --> 04:20.470
Her next target is Mr. Wei.

04:20.500 --> 04:21.500
No way.

04:22.590 --> 04:24.000
I already made this vixen

04:24.020 --> 04:25.290
get out of Purong.

04:25.330 --> 04:27.560
Seems I was too polite to her.

04:28.200 --> 04:29.320
I'll find someone

04:29.340 --> 04:30.660
to deal with her.

04:30.690 --> 04:33.350
I'll make her disappear
from the Shanghai Bund.

04:33.730 --> 04:35.330
Mrs. Wei, don't be angry yet.

04:35.500 --> 04:37.250
I have something else here.

04:37.280 --> 04:38.480
Please have a listen.

04:39.650 --> 04:44.650
[Recording]

04:40.680 --> 04:43.030
This little guy is so good.

04:43.620 --> 04:44.740
My baby.

04:45.090 --> 04:46.760
You already have a son and a daughter.

04:46.760 --> 04:48.280
And your wife is so fierce.

04:48.390 --> 04:50.290
Will you love our baby?

04:50.500 --> 04:51.960
Don't worry about that bitch.

04:51.960 --> 04:52.760
Rest assured.

04:53.180 --> 04:55.130
Once Purong is acquired by Kuanli,

04:55.190 --> 04:57.970
I'll take the money

04:58.159 --> 04:59.750
and take you and the baby

04:59.840 --> 05:01.280
abroad

05:01.300 --> 05:02.250
to live a good life.

05:02.250 --> 05:03.040
We three will enjoy

05:03.040 --> 05:04.190
the family happiness

05:04.190 --> 05:06.760
together.

05:06.790 --> 05:08.790
Shameless!

05:11.720 --> 05:13.860
Mrs. Wei, don't be angry.

05:14.010 --> 05:16.130
I understand how you feel right now.

05:16.150 --> 05:18.880
I have experienced everything
you are going through.

05:18.880 --> 05:20.710
Lu Zhenzhen is despicable,

05:20.730 --> 05:21.870
but

05:22.060 --> 05:24.540
a husband's betrayal is more painful

05:24.610 --> 05:26.040
and unbearable.

05:26.060 --> 05:27.100
No wonder

05:27.260 --> 05:28.990
Wei is always

05:29.010 --> 05:30.740
badmouthing you in front of me.

05:31.190 --> 05:31.830
It turns out

05:31.830 --> 05:32.950
he and that vixen

05:32.950 --> 05:34.510
hooked up a long time ago.

05:35.080 --> 05:35.890
Xu Miyu.

05:36.960 --> 05:37.720
How should we

05:38.330 --> 05:40.450
punish this adulterous couple?

05:48.280 --> 05:48.930
[Purong Hotel]

05:49.980 --> 05:52.270
[Purong Hotel]

05:50.340 --> 05:51.070
Mr. Xue.

05:51.560 --> 05:52.159
By the way,

05:52.390 --> 05:54.710
I saw a package for Mr. Wei in the lobby.

05:54.750 --> 05:56.310
Do you want to sign for it?

05:56.990 --> 05:57.430
Okay.

06:00.990 --> 06:04.130
[Internal Office] [Convention Center]

06:13.050 --> 06:13.990
Yes.

06:14.170 --> 06:15.650
Didn't I tell you not to disturb me?

06:15.650 --> 06:16.330
Mr. Wei.

06:19.680 --> 06:20.940
I'll call you back.

06:24.750 --> 06:25.480
Mr. Ji.

06:27.110 --> 06:28.440
What a rare guest.

06:29.140 --> 06:30.070
Long time no see.

06:30.480 --> 06:32.170
Where are you working lately?

06:33.610 --> 06:35.030
You're forgetful, Mr. Wei.

06:35.030 --> 06:36.470
I was fired.

06:36.500 --> 06:38.360
Which hotel would dare to hire me?

06:38.920 --> 06:40.240
Sorry, I forgot.

06:42.120 --> 06:43.360
You're

06:43.390 --> 06:44.950
too impulsive.

06:45.300 --> 06:46.980
But it's understandable.

06:47.000 --> 06:48.210
That's about love, huh?

06:48.210 --> 06:49.560
Ever since ancient times,

06:49.560 --> 06:51.440
men have gone mad for beauty.

06:54.680 --> 06:56.670
Thank you for understanding, Mr. Wei.

06:56.670 --> 06:57.850
But to be honest,

06:58.450 --> 06:59.600
I do regret it a bit.

06:59.920 --> 07:01.590
Regret now?

07:03.100 --> 07:04.260
For what?

07:07.130 --> 07:09.490
I regret doing something unnecessary.

07:12.040 --> 07:12.970
What do you mean?

07:15.270 --> 07:16.600
Actually, the spyware

07:16.750 --> 07:17.950
on Xu Miyu's phone

07:17.950 --> 07:19.190
was installed by you.

07:19.550 --> 07:21.460
The listening device in Marcos' room

07:21.460 --> 07:23.190
was also installed by your man.

07:23.970 --> 07:26.210
I suggest you stop before it's too late

07:26.700 --> 07:30.500
and take the initiative to tell
the facts to the investigation team.

07:30.660 --> 07:33.200
That way, you might still have a way out.

07:33.530 --> 07:36.060
Using the investigation team
to pressure me?

07:36.610 --> 07:37.940
Try to scare me?

07:37.970 --> 07:39.830
Don't shed crocodile tears here.

07:40.520 --> 07:42.159
The spyware on Xu Miyu's phone

07:42.159 --> 07:43.830
is an undeniable fact.

07:43.940 --> 07:44.630
The listening device

07:44.630 --> 07:46.890
was also planted in Marcos's room by her.

07:47.050 --> 07:47.840
Listen.

07:47.870 --> 07:49.220
Xu Miyu can't escape
the hotel's punishment

07:49.220 --> 07:51.220
just because the video was deleted.

07:51.280 --> 07:53.300
There will definitely be more evidence.

07:53.300 --> 07:54.530
Once I find it,

07:54.780 --> 07:56.340
she'll be fired.

07:57.700 --> 07:58.620
Well,

07:59.230 --> 08:01.430
I have to let you listen to the evidence.

08:02.040 --> 08:02.900
What evidence?

08:06.410 --> 08:07.410
Honey?

08:22.750 --> 08:23.640
Honey?

08:25.380 --> 08:26.070
Honey?

08:26.880 --> 08:28.630
Where are you going
with your things?

08:28.630 --> 08:30.050
I'm going to my mom's.

08:30.080 --> 08:32.010
Her lumbar disc is acting up again.

08:33.740 --> 08:34.320
Is it serious?

08:34.320 --> 08:36.360
Do you want me to go with you to see her?

08:36.360 --> 08:37.120
No, no.

08:37.400 --> 08:39.860
Just focus on your hotel business.

08:41.409 --> 08:43.620
How's that matter going on your end?

08:43.770 --> 08:44.690
Which one?

08:45.150 --> 08:46.390
What Niu Qiankun has asked you

08:46.390 --> 08:47.870
to help with.

08:48.070 --> 08:48.790
Didn't you help him

08:48.790 --> 08:50.320
get Liberty Group's

08:50.320 --> 08:51.330
base price?

08:51.350 --> 08:52.750
Did he give you the money?

08:53.150 --> 08:54.390
Not yet.

08:54.870 --> 08:56.120
As soon as the listening device
was planted,

08:56.120 --> 08:58.120
it was discovered by Liberty Group.

08:58.210 --> 08:59.550
It caused a huge uproar.

08:59.680 --> 09:01.920
Since Yuntian Group
is delaying the bid award,

09:01.920 --> 09:03.770
Niu Qiankun refuses to pay.

09:04.020 --> 09:06.150
Or I would have gone with you to see Mom.

09:07.470 --> 09:09.790
Niu Qiankun is not keeping his word.

09:10.150 --> 09:11.630
Wasn't it agreed that

09:11.650 --> 09:14.560
your task would be regarded as finished

09:14.950 --> 09:16.690
after you planted the listening device
in the other party's room

09:16.690 --> 09:18.170
and let him know their base price?

09:18.170 --> 09:19.460
He wants to renege, right?

09:19.460 --> 09:20.520
I'll question him.

09:21.240 --> 09:22.620
Alright, don't be angry.

09:22.620 --> 09:23.390
Calm down,

09:23.390 --> 09:24.480
and take it easy.

09:26.560 --> 09:28.440
I'm partly to blame for this.

09:28.470 --> 09:29.890
My subordinates didn't do a good job,

09:29.890 --> 09:31.620
so the bid can't be awarded now.

09:31.810 --> 09:33.560
You know Niu Qiankun well.

09:33.680 --> 09:34.550
If he can't make money,

09:34.550 --> 09:35.790
how could he pay me?

09:36.080 --> 09:37.380
But don't worry, Honey.

09:37.380 --> 09:38.930
I'm trying to find a way these two days

09:38.930 --> 09:40.130
to get Yuntian Group

09:40.150 --> 09:41.920
to award the bid as soon as possible.

09:41.920 --> 09:43.340
Once this is settled,

09:43.430 --> 09:45.420
I'll take you, our daughter and son

09:45.750 --> 09:47.030
to immigrate to Australia.

09:47.030 --> 09:48.560
We can retire and chill out,

09:48.790 --> 09:49.940
lying on the beach every day,

09:49.940 --> 09:50.550
eating barbecue,

09:50.550 --> 09:51.550
and drinking.

09:51.870 --> 09:53.130
What a wonderful life!

09:54.670 --> 09:57.390
That subordinate you mentioned

09:57.510 --> 09:59.790
is Lu Zhenzhen, that vixen, right?

10:02.630 --> 10:03.950
Her?

10:04.180 --> 10:05.790
Don't misunderstand, Honey.

10:05.790 --> 10:07.790
She's just a tool to me.

10:09.310 --> 10:10.630
You know,

10:11.170 --> 10:12.200
your family's

10:12.230 --> 10:14.050
Kaixin, Qian Xun,

10:14.080 --> 10:15.100
and Huang Chengmin

10:15.100 --> 10:16.640
were all taken away by Ji.

10:16.670 --> 10:18.800
I really have no one left to work for me.

10:19.630 --> 10:21.150
Is this woman reliable?

10:21.960 --> 10:24.590
They say she's very scheming.

10:27.560 --> 10:30.010
This woman just cares about money.

10:30.090 --> 10:32.890
I promised her a little money.

10:32.920 --> 10:35.160
She'll handle all these things.

10:35.190 --> 10:38.440
Even if we fail,
she'll take the blame for me.

10:38.660 --> 10:41.520
Isn't that killing two birds
with one stone, Honey?

10:41.950 --> 10:43.940
You men are all bad.

10:45.270 --> 10:46.880
I treat other women badly.

10:46.910 --> 10:48.510
Isn't that how it should be?

10:48.590 --> 10:51.170
I only love you.

10:51.810 --> 10:52.570
Honey.

11:03.510 --> 11:05.170
It's no use trying to snatch it.

11:05.170 --> 11:06.720
This is just for you to hear.

11:06.840 --> 11:07.830
A backup of the recording

11:07.830 --> 11:10.560
has already been sent
to the investigation team.

11:13.440 --> 11:14.640
What does this prove?

11:16.270 --> 11:17.480
What does this prove?

11:17.970 --> 11:20.510
It's just a private chat
between me and my wife at home.

11:20.510 --> 11:21.990
Who knows if it's true or false?

11:21.990 --> 11:24.110
Will the investigation team
call the police to arrest me over this?

11:24.110 --> 11:24.910
You're too naive.

11:24.910 --> 11:26.390
Whether you can be arrested or not

11:26.390 --> 11:27.480
is up to the police.

11:27.800 --> 11:28.560
Besides,

11:28.590 --> 11:32.520
the anonymous email connected
to the listening device has been found.

11:32.770 --> 11:33.570
What?

11:34.410 --> 11:36.010
It's right in your computer.

11:41.890 --> 11:42.760
Mr. Wei,

11:42.780 --> 11:44.580
the investigation team is here.

11:52.800 --> 11:53.440
Mr. Wei,

11:54.350 --> 11:55.880
come back with us for a chat.

11:55.970 --> 11:58.100
Don't believe in Ji Feng's nonsense.

11:58.310 --> 12:00.140
This has nothing to do with me.

12:02.060 --> 12:03.520
Please escort Mr. Wei out.

12:09.330 --> 12:11.320
What right do you have to take me away?

12:11.320 --> 12:14.010
I am the general manager of Purong Hotel.

12:14.910 --> 12:15.790
Look,

12:17.180 --> 12:18.490
do I have the right?

12:21.640 --> 12:22.580
Aunt.

12:23.240 --> 12:24.770
Aunt, you're finally here.

12:24.920 --> 12:25.920
Please save me.

12:26.450 --> 12:27.550
Ji Feng is framing me.

12:27.550 --> 12:28.360
He is setting me up.

12:28.360 --> 12:29.810
I didn't do anything, Aunt.

12:29.810 --> 12:30.870
You have to help me.

12:31.050 --> 12:32.910
I have already seen the evidence.

12:34.160 --> 12:35.280
You dare to do it,

12:35.970 --> 12:37.430
but don't dare to admit it?

12:39.150 --> 12:40.360
Aunt.

12:42.030 --> 12:42.750
Aunt.

12:44.010 --> 12:45.820
Ji Feng forced me.

12:46.550 --> 12:49.630
He made things difficult
for me again and again,

12:50.360 --> 12:51.820
so I took a desperate risk.

12:51.870 --> 12:52.530
Aunt,

12:52.960 --> 12:54.400
please save me, Aunt.

12:54.740 --> 12:55.750
The investigation team works for you.

12:55.750 --> 12:56.630
As long as you say a word,

12:56.630 --> 12:57.870
they won't make things difficult for me.

12:57.870 --> 12:59.390
I can't let them take me away.

12:59.390 --> 12:59.870
Aunt,

12:59.870 --> 13:01.240
didn't you say

13:01.270 --> 13:03.300
you would leave Purong Hotel to me?

13:03.500 --> 13:04.190
Aunt.

13:07.150 --> 13:08.120
I thought

13:09.460 --> 13:10.970
you would repent.

13:21.290 --> 13:22.290
Call the police.

13:24.160 --> 13:27.040
Let him be punished by the law.

13:28.140 --> 13:29.290
Aunt, don't call the police.

13:29.290 --> 13:29.760
Aunt,

13:29.790 --> 13:30.520
Aunt.

13:30.980 --> 13:31.680
Aunt,

13:32.330 --> 13:34.600
why did you choose him in the end?

13:34.620 --> 13:36.080
I am your family.

13:36.080 --> 13:36.720
Aunt.

13:37.580 --> 13:38.300
Aunt.

13:38.950 --> 13:40.430
Aunt, please forgive me.

13:40.450 --> 13:42.570
Give me another chance, Aunt.

13:43.040 --> 13:44.070
Aunt.

14:33.640 --> 14:34.590
Hello, Mr. Ji.

14:36.450 --> 14:37.730
Hello, Mr. Ji.

14:51.940 --> 14:52.700
Madam.

15:06.030 --> 15:07.360
Welcome back.

15:08.540 --> 15:11.420
The future of Purong Hotel
is in your hands.

15:13.700 --> 15:14.600
Madam.

15:14.920 --> 15:16.820
There are fewer than two weeks left.

15:16.820 --> 15:17.940
I will do my best.

15:17.970 --> 15:19.100
I won't let you down.

15:22.060 --> 15:23.060
Hello, everyone.

15:23.490 --> 15:25.150
I want to share some good news.

15:25.560 --> 15:26.610
Purong Hotel

15:26.630 --> 15:29.300
is getting back on track step by step.

15:29.450 --> 15:31.680
But if we want to improve our performance,

15:31.680 --> 15:34.210
we still need everyone's concerted
efforts.

15:34.240 --> 15:35.430
Are you confident?

15:35.460 --> 15:36.820
-Yes.
-Yes.

15:38.240 --> 15:39.550
Not loud enough.

15:39.570 --> 15:40.810
-Yes.
-Yes.

15:54.270 --> 15:56.390
No matter

15:56.410 --> 15:58.940
which position you rotate to in the hotel,

15:58.970 --> 16:00.520
remember the slogan,

16:00.540 --> 16:01.940
"Making guests feel at home".

16:01.940 --> 16:04.420
It's the service tenet of Purong Hotel.

16:04.440 --> 16:08.100
I hope that in every service you provide,

16:08.130 --> 16:11.770
you can understand the meaning
of working as a hotel worker.

16:11.790 --> 16:15.150
This is also the value Purong offers you.

16:40.810 --> 16:41.680
Here's to our cooperation.

16:41.680 --> 16:43.210
Here's to our cooperation.

16:45.400 --> 16:47.080
[Contract]

16:51.380 --> 16:52.850
[Contract]

17:00.700 --> 17:01.760
Congratulations.

17:02.910 --> 17:04.050
Thank you.

17:04.079 --> 17:06.040
Thank you for your persistence.

17:06.060 --> 17:07.720
You risked your own reputation
and the hotel's reputation

17:07.720 --> 17:08.829
to fight for

17:09.010 --> 17:11.300
the interests

17:11.650 --> 17:13.050
for me and Liberty Group.

17:13.859 --> 17:14.510
Thank you.

17:14.540 --> 17:15.819
We should thank you.

17:15.960 --> 17:16.609
Really.

17:16.640 --> 17:18.920
At Purong Hotel's most difficult time,

17:19.020 --> 17:20.220
you made

17:20.240 --> 17:22.440
a long-term deal with us.

17:22.619 --> 17:24.359
It means a lot to us.

17:25.660 --> 17:27.900
I genuinely like Purong Hotel.

17:29.000 --> 17:30.930
This is also the highest praise

17:30.960 --> 17:32.630
for the values we have always adhered to.

17:32.630 --> 17:35.020
We will always serve you wholeheartedly

17:35.050 --> 17:37.230
and serve everyone
who steps into Purong Hotel.

17:37.230 --> 17:37.790
Good.

17:38.350 --> 17:39.750
I believe in what you say.

17:41.460 --> 17:42.660
Glad to work with you.

17:43.070 --> 17:43.670
Thank you.

17:43.790 --> 17:44.970
It's what we should do.

17:44.970 --> 17:46.870
Thank you. Thank you.

17:50.400 --> 17:51.960
Welcome.

17:52.640 --> 17:53.590
This way.

18:00.720 --> 18:02.650
Welcome to stay at Purong Hotel.

18:02.750 --> 18:04.070
I found you

18:04.070 --> 18:05.720
booked a luxury king room.

18:05.720 --> 18:06.160
Right?

18:06.160 --> 18:06.750
Yes.

18:07.220 --> 18:08.300
Is the ninth floor okay?

18:08.300 --> 18:08.930
Yes.

18:18.310 --> 18:19.350
Welcome.

18:24.720 --> 18:26.090
Welcome.

18:29.960 --> 18:30.740
This way, please.

18:30.740 --> 18:31.350
Hello.

18:31.370 --> 18:32.900
Your service is really good.

18:32.900 --> 18:34.200
I heard you have authentic

18:34.200 --> 18:35.350
Suzhou-style boat pastries, right?

18:35.350 --> 18:36.550
Yes, I'll take you there later.

18:36.550 --> 18:37.960
Great. Thank you.

18:37.980 --> 18:39.040
That's wonderful.

18:44.520 --> 18:45.880
Hello, here is Blooming Flowers
and Full Moon.

18:45.880 --> 18:46.930
Enjoy your meal.

18:55.610 --> 18:57.540
Do you have any other specialties here?

18:57.540 --> 18:58.920
Please take a look here.

18:59.820 --> 19:01.880
Items like this one sell really well.

19:02.130 --> 19:03.200
I'll have an ice cream.

19:03.200 --> 19:03.840
Okay.

19:52.450 --> 19:56.200
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

19:59.830 --> 20:03.530
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

20:06.800 --> 20:10.760
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

20:09.720 --> 20:10.530
Thank you.

20:14.440 --> 20:18.340
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

20:14.610 --> 20:16.780
[Four Seasons Art Museum]

20:16.780 --> 20:19.070
[Four Seasons, an art feast]

20:19.240 --> 20:20.070
Are you looking for

20:20.070 --> 20:21.950
Amber Santos's
Four Seasons Art Exhibition?

20:21.900 --> 20:25.800
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

20:21.970 --> 20:23.000
Yes, that's it.

20:23.020 --> 20:25.070
This exhibition is indeed hard to find.

20:25.070 --> 20:26.550
It's in the art space on the eighth floor

20:26.550 --> 20:27.940
of the mall next door.

20:27.970 --> 20:29.120
There are posters up there.

20:29.120 --> 20:30.400
You'll see them when you get up there.

20:29.540 --> 20:33.570
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

20:30.400 --> 20:31.510
Just follow the directions.

20:31.510 --> 20:32.830
Okay, thank you.

20:32.830 --> 20:34.130
Glad to serve you.

20:34.770 --> 20:35.780
Mr. Tan.

20:36.880 --> 20:40.920
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

20:39.510 --> 20:41.060
You should keep this.

20:42.480 --> 20:44.300
Do you remember this exhibition?

20:44.300 --> 20:45.370
It's back in Shanghai

20:44.520 --> 20:48.270
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

20:45.850 --> 20:46.970
at the same place.

20:47.980 --> 20:49.740
I failed last year.

20:49.760 --> 20:51.560
I thought I'd never see it again.

20:51.860 --> 20:54.780
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

20:52.070 --> 20:53.470
Fate will bring you to it.

20:58.160 --> 21:04.010
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

20:59.060 --> 20:59.750
Miyu.

21:01.050 --> 21:02.530
Can I hug you again?

21:06.490 --> 21:09.720
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

21:13.110 --> 21:18.830
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

21:16.250 --> 21:16.850
Take care

21:19.750 --> 21:20.840
Mr. Tan.

21:20.010 --> 21:22.870
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

21:21.200 --> 21:22.330
Have a safe journey.

21:37.340 --> 21:40.880
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

21:43.640 --> 21:49.490
♪ I feel reluctant to forgive you
and there's nothing I can do ♪

21:52.230 --> 21:57.660
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

21:59.430 --> 22:05.340
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to you,
and I can't breathe ♪

22:06.370 --> 22:09.120
♪ I've cut myself some slack ♪

22:10.610 --> 22:11.600
Miyu.

22:11.820 --> 22:13.450
Why are you in such a hurry?

22:12.370 --> 22:14.690
[Math][Chinese]

22:18.350 --> 22:21.350
Are you going to take
the Adult College Entrance Exam?

22:22.650 --> 22:23.780
It's a long story.

22:23.810 --> 22:26.630
I used to think that since the hotel
provided food and accommodation,

22:26.630 --> 22:28.600
I could just scrape by here.

22:28.630 --> 22:30.240
But then I saw you.

22:30.260 --> 22:31.910
You were always so motivated,

22:31.910 --> 22:34.310
going from an attendant
to a sales manager.

22:34.430 --> 22:35.680
I figured

22:35.790 --> 22:37.490
if I could work hard

22:37.290 --> 22:39.200
♪ Life is full of ♪

22:37.520 --> 22:39.630
for a better future for myself.

22:40.250 --> 22:42.980
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

22:40.640 --> 22:43.530
So, I borrowed Luo Qingping's books

22:43.560 --> 22:45.060
and signed up for night school.

22:44.440 --> 22:48.290
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

22:45.080 --> 22:46.710
When I finish studying,

22:46.740 --> 22:48.110
I can take the exam.

22:48.380 --> 22:49.500
You can definitely do it.

22:49.500 --> 22:50.130
Good luck.

22:49.870 --> 22:51.950
♪ All those confusions ♪

22:50.680 --> 22:52.520
I'm going to be late for my class.

22:52.470 --> 22:56.190
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

22:52.540 --> 22:53.720
Let's chat another day.

22:53.720 --> 22:54.850
Okay, go ahead.

22:57.060 --> 23:01.060
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

23:00.290 --> 23:03.090
[2025 Sum]

23:04.460 --> 23:06.960
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

23:07.990 --> 23:10.110
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

23:11.130 --> 23:12.320
[General Manager's Office]

23:11.740 --> 23:15.530
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

23:17.100 --> 23:19.110
♪ Busy and restless ♪

23:19.660 --> 23:23.460
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

23:24.460 --> 23:28.600
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

23:30.380 --> 23:33.040
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

23:34.070 --> 23:36.180
♪ Don't look back ♪

23:34.200 --> 23:36.580
Book me a flight to the Maldives.

23:36.870 --> 23:38.750
This place is too stuffy.

23:37.060 --> 23:39.120
♪ I've already learned ♪

23:38.960 --> 23:39.800
Mr. Duan Jr..

23:39.630 --> 23:43.430
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

23:39.830 --> 23:42.690
should we send
this performance report to Mr. Duan?

23:43.410 --> 23:44.210
What's the rush?

23:44.150 --> 23:45.900
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

23:44.890 --> 23:46.600
Wait until the dividends come out,

23:46.600 --> 23:50.790
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

23:46.640 --> 23:48.460
and then send them
to the old man together,

23:48.460 --> 23:50.870
lest he say
I'm wasting my time here.

23:51.520 --> 23:54.430
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

23:51.640 --> 23:54.100
Will you still live here
after you come back?

23:54.440 --> 23:55.200
Yes.

23:55.350 --> 23:57.680
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

23:55.560 --> 23:57.870
I love the food here anyway.

23:58.380 --> 24:00.330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

24:13.090 --> 24:15.580
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

24:16.390 --> 24:18.390
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

24:20.370 --> 24:24.570
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

24:20.830 --> 24:22.500
[Lu Zhenzhen, Sales Department,
Purong Hotel]

24:25.890 --> 24:27.980
♪ Busy and restless ♪

24:28.290 --> 24:32.270
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

24:33.070 --> 24:37.330
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

24:39.280 --> 24:40.960
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

24:41.740 --> 24:46.190
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

24:46.660 --> 24:49.470
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

24:50.600 --> 24:52.920
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

24:53.520 --> 24:55.330
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

25:02.440 --> 25:03.580
You must be happy,

25:04.360 --> 25:06.420
finally kicking me out of this hotel.

25:07.720 --> 25:08.980
You're overthinking.

25:09.630 --> 25:12.490
I never wanted a life-and-death
struggle with you.

25:12.660 --> 25:17.050
We are fundamentally different people.

25:17.220 --> 25:17.850
No.

25:19.180 --> 25:21.240
That time I saw you at the coffee shop,

25:22.200 --> 25:24.470
when I saw you bluffing in front of me,

25:24.510 --> 25:27.840
I knew we were exactly
the same kind of people.

25:30.170 --> 25:31.640
We both desperately crave love,

25:31.640 --> 25:33.550
and desperately crave attention.

25:33.550 --> 25:35.020
But the difference is,

25:35.260 --> 25:36.520
you're hypocritical,

25:36.850 --> 25:38.790
pretending you want nothing,

25:38.810 --> 25:40.320
yet taking it secretly,

25:40.440 --> 25:42.880
making everyone think
you're a good person.

25:42.880 --> 25:44.060
And me?

25:45.680 --> 25:46.900
I rely on myself

25:47.230 --> 25:48.640
to change my family

25:48.640 --> 25:50.080
and my background.

25:50.370 --> 25:51.840
If fate can't give me something,

25:51.840 --> 25:53.790
I will get it back on my own.

25:53.830 --> 25:54.590
What did I do wrong?

25:54.590 --> 25:55.750
Am I wrong?

25:56.880 --> 25:58.870
I never said I didn't want it.

25:59.530 --> 26:00.460
On the contrary,

26:00.830 --> 26:02.220
I'll get the career,

26:02.240 --> 26:03.150
happiness,

26:03.320 --> 26:04.480
and everything I want,

26:04.480 --> 26:05.970
through my own efforts.

26:06.000 --> 26:06.920
I started from zero,

26:06.920 --> 26:08.270
took steps by steps,

26:08.660 --> 26:10.460
and grasped them in my own hands,

26:11.240 --> 26:12.330
because I know

26:12.360 --> 26:15.400
all shortcuts in this world are detours.

26:16.090 --> 26:18.200
Everything you get by hook or by crook

26:19.270 --> 26:20.310
will come back

26:20.780 --> 26:22.540
to bite you in another way.

26:23.390 --> 26:24.950
Don't blame everything

26:24.970 --> 26:25.840
on family,

26:26.270 --> 26:27.200
and background.

26:27.720 --> 26:29.450
That's just where we came from.

26:29.830 --> 26:33.160
It's not your get-out-of-jail-free card
to do whatever you want.

26:33.160 --> 26:35.510
Don't think you can hurt others

26:36.200 --> 26:38.240
just because others hurt you.

27:13.610 --> 27:18.010
[15 years ago]

27:38.170 --> 27:38.810
Mom.

27:39.330 --> 27:40.290
Zhenzhen.

27:40.960 --> 27:41.930
It's so late.

27:42.010 --> 27:43.410
How did you find this place?

27:43.410 --> 27:45.450
There are mice in the school dorm.

27:45.480 --> 27:47.080
My classmates all went home.

27:47.960 --> 27:49.590
Can I sleep here tonight?

27:52.400 --> 27:53.640
That won't do.

27:53.660 --> 27:55.280
This is not my home.

27:55.330 --> 27:56.750
You should go back.

27:57.780 --> 27:58.450
Mom.

27:59.350 --> 28:00.510
I'm begging you.

28:00.890 --> 28:02.290
I have nowhere else to go.

28:02.910 --> 28:04.700
Who is it at this hour?

28:05.570 --> 28:06.460
It's fine.

28:06.480 --> 28:07.800
I'm coming.

28:12.070 --> 28:13.160
Stop being stubborn.

28:13.160 --> 28:15.360
He doesn't know about you right now.

28:15.420 --> 28:16.220
Be good.

28:16.240 --> 28:17.270
Just leave.

28:18.710 --> 28:21.380
Is it comfortable to abandon
your daughter and remarry?

28:21.380 --> 28:22.830
You chose a man instead of me.

28:22.830 --> 28:24.150
What kind of mother are you?

28:24.150 --> 28:24.750
Otherwise,

28:24.750 --> 28:26.530
how would I afford your food,
clothes, and school?

28:26.530 --> 28:28.930
Do you still think
you're a rich young lady?

28:30.130 --> 28:31.370
You'd blame your dad.

28:31.820 --> 28:34.280
His perfectly good business
went bankrupt.

28:34.850 --> 28:36.400
He just ran away,

28:36.600 --> 28:38.610
leaving us with a lot of debt

28:38.640 --> 28:40.300
and not even a house to live in.

28:41.160 --> 28:42.160
I took you with me,

28:42.300 --> 28:43.310
getting a bite to eat here

28:43.310 --> 28:44.030
and a bed to sleep there,

28:44.030 --> 28:44.920
surviving until today.

28:44.920 --> 28:46.520
What else do you want from me?

28:48.720 --> 28:49.370
Mom.

28:51.080 --> 28:52.850
I can skip the college entrance exam.

28:52.850 --> 28:54.810
I can work and make money.

28:55.350 --> 28:57.140
Can we be together

28:57.330 --> 28:58.660
as a family like before?

29:00.830 --> 29:02.530
If you want to be like before,

29:04.020 --> 29:06.280
you have to be stronger than anyone else.

29:06.600 --> 29:07.970
You have to learn how to climb higher,

29:07.970 --> 29:09.590
to fight, and to grab.

29:09.680 --> 29:12.220
You must make everyone
who looked down on you regret it.

29:12.220 --> 29:12.970
Understand?

29:33.000 --> 29:34.030
Lu Zhenzhen.

29:35.850 --> 29:37.430
You will climb very high.

29:38.960 --> 29:40.440
You'll become very rich.

29:42.750 --> 29:44.690
You will have your own home.

29:46.590 --> 29:48.070
No one can drive you away.

29:58.780 --> 30:08.340
[Purong Hotel]

30:09.370 --> 30:10.670
Are you Lu Zhenzhen?

30:10.920 --> 30:11.670
[Police]

30:12.530 --> 30:14.710
You are suspected of instigating
the installation of wiretapping devices

30:14.710 --> 30:16.370
to steal commercial secrets.

30:16.430 --> 30:17.610
Come with us.

30:18.500 --> 30:27.490
[Lu Zhenzhen was arrested for tapping]

30:36.250 --> 30:38.450
It's a pity I didn't realize until today

30:39.270 --> 30:41.080
how completely wrong

30:41.260 --> 30:42.930
my mom's words were.

30:43.570 --> 30:45.710
I finally paid the price

30:45.740 --> 30:46.830
for my stupidity.

30:46.920 --> 30:51.590
[Public Security]

30:53.140 --> 30:56.110
[Shadow puppets]

30:53.400 --> 30:55.070
This bridge we're on now

30:55.070 --> 30:57.550
is a very famous local landmark.

30:57.590 --> 30:58.720
Watch your step, everyone.

30:58.720 --> 31:01.320
There are stairs
and it's slippery in the rain.

31:02.720 --> 31:04.140
Come on, follow me.

31:06.170 --> 31:07.110
You are the tour guide, right?

31:07.110 --> 31:07.630
Yes.

31:07.650 --> 31:08.880
I'm here to lead the way.

31:08.880 --> 31:10.460
Please follow me this way.

31:10.490 --> 31:11.450
Okay, thank you.

31:11.890 --> 31:13.360
Watch your step. It's a bit slippery.

31:13.360 --> 31:13.780
Okay.

31:13.800 --> 31:15.960
Come on, everyone,
please stay close to me.

31:15.960 --> 31:17.280
Come on, everyone, this way please.

31:17.280 --> 31:18.110
We are now going

31:18.110 --> 31:20.570
to a very famous local restaurant.

31:20.590 --> 31:22.500
Alright, watch your step.

31:22.720 --> 31:24.110
It's a bit slippery.

31:24.910 --> 31:26.770
The road is slippery, be careful.

31:27.140 --> 31:30.580
[Xiumei Restaurant]

31:34.180 --> 31:35.530
The star anise is here.

31:35.760 --> 31:37.000
Bring it in quickly.

31:38.850 --> 31:40.280
Perfect timing this time.

31:40.280 --> 31:42.140
The freshest batch of star anise.

31:42.810 --> 31:44.560
How can dried goods be fresh?

31:45.310 --> 31:46.790
It's newly arrived.

31:46.790 --> 31:48.480
Doesn't that mean it's fresh?

31:49.170 --> 31:50.930
Can't I just say a few words?

31:51.330 --> 31:53.640
Hurry out and clear the tables.

31:53.670 --> 31:55.360
The big group is coming soon.

31:55.720 --> 31:57.310
We have time. No rush.

31:58.250 --> 31:59.900
Please come inside, everyone.

31:59.900 --> 32:00.510
Come on.

32:00.510 --> 32:01.750
Hurry up!

32:01.750 --> 32:02.920
-Get out.
-So much sweat.

32:02.920 --> 32:04.050
Let me rest for a bit.

32:04.250 --> 32:06.390
Who makes the money in this family now?

32:08.220 --> 32:08.790
You do.

32:08.960 --> 32:09.550
Go.

32:09.570 --> 32:10.220
Okay.

32:14.180 --> 32:15.750
Come in and sit anywhere.

32:15.750 --> 32:17.480
I'll get you some water.

32:20.390 --> 32:21.070
How is it going?

32:21.070 --> 32:21.950
Are you almost done?

32:21.950 --> 32:22.760
Almost.

32:22.790 --> 32:24.700
I will check it for you when you're done.

32:24.700 --> 32:25.570
Okay, Mom.

32:35.970 --> 32:37.800
The music stops, and the crowd disperses.

32:37.800 --> 32:39.930
When the music stops, people do leave.

32:40.800 --> 32:42.630
I thought you would stay here,

32:44.180 --> 32:45.380
always.

32:47.560 --> 32:49.380
That doesn't sound like

32:49.720 --> 32:51.590
the past footless bird

32:51.590 --> 32:53.190
who always loved wandering.

32:54.330 --> 32:56.150
I always thought that

32:56.170 --> 32:58.590
providing a home
away from home for others,

32:59.720 --> 33:01.030
and keeping yourself always

33:01.030 --> 33:02.960
on the way to the next destination,

33:03.040 --> 33:05.710
is the destiny of a hotelier.

33:06.790 --> 33:08.450
I only have to pursue success,

33:09.030 --> 33:10.160
know no attachment,

33:10.520 --> 33:11.780
and have no stability.

33:13.400 --> 33:14.400
But now?

33:15.550 --> 33:16.400
I know

33:16.420 --> 33:19.060
there are many important things in life

33:19.520 --> 33:21.920
that achievements can't measure.

33:29.790 --> 33:30.790
I told you.

33:31.900 --> 33:33.880
Xu Miyu is no ordinary person.

33:34.690 --> 33:36.170
In just one year,

33:36.510 --> 33:38.770
she turned you from a boring workaholic

33:39.200 --> 33:41.270
into someone more down-to-earth.

33:45.650 --> 33:46.780
What about you, Rui?

33:46.960 --> 33:49.360
Have you really decided to wander outside?

33:51.190 --> 33:53.140
I wanted to leave Purong

33:53.640 --> 33:55.840
to find another place for retirement.

33:57.590 --> 33:59.650
But after working with you for a year,

34:00.610 --> 34:02.100
I found that my life

34:02.710 --> 34:05.170
has more choices
than just running in place.

34:07.690 --> 34:09.550
So I want to leave my comfort zone.

34:10.150 --> 34:13.170
I want to fight for myself once more.

34:16.449 --> 34:17.170
Say no more.

34:18.170 --> 34:19.610
I wish you

34:19.969 --> 34:22.030
a safe journey on your new adventure.

34:22.150 --> 34:23.370
If you have any problems,

34:23.370 --> 34:25.300
come back to Purong Hotel anytime.

34:32.570 --> 34:35.000
Home is where the heart is at peace.

34:41.300 --> 34:42.530
[Are you off work?]

34:41.710 --> 34:43.199
[Ji Feng]

34:52.050 --> 34:52.760
[Mail]

34:52.760 --> 34:54.630
[EHL Conditional Offer]

34:54.650 --> 34:56.020
[EHL Conditional Offer]

34:57.650 --> 34:58.730
[Conditional Offer]

35:03.770 --> 35:05.430
[Conditional Offer]

35:05.470 --> 35:07.100
[Ji Feng]

35:07.570 --> 35:11.590
[Are you off work?]

35:11.620 --> 35:12.730
[I...]

35:34.920 --> 35:36.000
Look at that star.

35:36.020 --> 35:36.860
So bright.

35:39.900 --> 35:42.110
Does every star in the sky

35:42.510 --> 35:43.920
have its own trajectory?

35:46.310 --> 35:48.020
Only by leaving where you are,

35:48.920 --> 35:51.000
can you go to a wider world.

35:56.730 --> 35:58.350
I'm leaving Purong.

36:00.840 --> 36:03.250
Is it because of our relationship?

36:05.250 --> 36:06.730
There's no explicit rule

36:06.760 --> 36:08.950
against office romances.

36:09.310 --> 36:12.060
Besides, I've already
taken over Purong Hotel.

36:12.290 --> 36:14.390
I can handle everything well.

36:15.000 --> 36:16.670
Your career has just begun.

36:16.670 --> 36:17.910
I don't want our relationship

36:17.910 --> 36:19.500
to affect your career.

36:20.010 --> 36:20.930
Trust me.

36:23.520 --> 36:26.280
I was admitted to EHL

36:26.280 --> 36:27.280
in Switzerland.

36:28.190 --> 36:29.710
I want to study abroad,

36:29.730 --> 36:31.410
just like you did.

36:32.490 --> 36:33.850
EHL?

36:46.680 --> 36:47.760
Have you decided?

36:52.080 --> 36:53.850
After being with you,

36:54.360 --> 36:56.630
I feel that I'm getting stronger

36:56.650 --> 36:57.940
and more confident.

36:58.630 --> 37:00.400
Through your eyes,

37:00.550 --> 37:02.980
I saw more possibilities for myself.

37:03.840 --> 37:06.440
I want to be brave for once

37:06.470 --> 37:07.960
and pursue my dream.

37:09.400 --> 37:12.030
I want to pursue a fuller life.

37:16.480 --> 37:17.610
I made this decision on my own

37:17.610 --> 37:19.710
without discussing it with you.

37:19.730 --> 37:21.290
Are you mad at me?

37:25.760 --> 37:26.990
In my heart,

37:26.400 --> 37:28.300
♪ Life is full of ♪

37:27.070 --> 37:29.000
you've always been a shining star.

37:29.110 --> 37:30.580
You are brave and hardworking.

37:29.370 --> 37:32.090
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

37:33.330 --> 37:35.770
I'll just wait here for you to come back.

37:33.550 --> 37:37.400
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

37:36.850 --> 37:37.770
Thank you.

37:38.350 --> 37:39.070
For what?

37:38.980 --> 37:41.050
♪ All those confusions ♪

37:41.310 --> 37:43.110
Thank you for everything
you've done for me.

37:41.570 --> 37:45.310
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

37:46.170 --> 37:50.370
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

37:48.100 --> 37:49.480
I used to think

37:49.510 --> 37:50.820
that we were completely

37:50.820 --> 37:52.490
from two different worlds.

37:53.570 --> 37:55.950
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

37:53.620 --> 37:54.900
I've felt inferior

37:55.020 --> 37:56.230
and I've run away.

37:57.100 --> 37:59.210
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

37:57.600 --> 38:00.310
I used to say you were condescending,

38:00.330 --> 38:01.810
but thinking about it now,

38:00.850 --> 38:04.740
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

38:02.370 --> 38:04.990
I knew it was just my pride acting up.

38:05.850 --> 38:09.080
I thought you were so excellent.

38:06.210 --> 38:08.330
♪ Busy and restless ♪

38:08.770 --> 38:12.570
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

38:10.650 --> 38:12.710
I was afraid you would look down on me,

38:12.820 --> 38:14.460
and I couldn't keep up with you.

38:13.570 --> 38:17.710
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

38:16.460 --> 38:18.110
But now I know

38:19.490 --> 38:22.150
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

38:19.630 --> 38:21.280
a good relationship is to

38:21.880 --> 38:24.110
make each other better.

38:23.180 --> 38:25.290
♪ Don't look back ♪

38:26.170 --> 38:28.230
♪ I've already learned ♪

38:27.980 --> 38:29.260
I should thank you too.

38:28.730 --> 38:32.530
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

38:30.030 --> 38:32.340
Thank you for enriching my life,

38:33.230 --> 38:34.710
so that I'm no longer

38:33.250 --> 38:35.000
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

38:34.730 --> 38:36.820
carrying a cold suitcase

38:35.710 --> 38:39.900
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

38:37.190 --> 38:39.680
from one hotel to another,

38:40.540 --> 38:41.450
but

38:40.660 --> 38:43.540
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

38:43.730 --> 38:45.120
have the warmth of a home.

38:44.450 --> 38:46.780
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

38:47.490 --> 38:49.440
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

38:47.520 --> 38:48.400
It also made me realize

38:48.400 --> 38:52.290
the stars on our heads are so beautiful.

38:53.860 --> 38:54.820
Thank you,

38:55.590 --> 38:57.900
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

38:55.760 --> 38:58.180
the gift of my life.

38:58.350 --> 39:00.540
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

39:02.790 --> 39:06.760
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

39:05.670 --> 39:06.910
Even though

39:07.710 --> 39:09.890
we're so different

39:08.300 --> 39:10.360
♪ Busy and restless ♪

39:10.800 --> 39:12.510
and have different paths to take,

39:11.060 --> 39:14.730
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

39:13.740 --> 39:16.160
I believe more and more now

39:15.620 --> 39:19.640
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

39:16.880 --> 39:18.610
that as long as we are like this,

39:18.860 --> 39:20.150
holding hands,

39:20.510 --> 39:21.800
no matter how far we go,

39:21.870 --> 39:23.230
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

39:22.450 --> 39:24.370
we can always give each other strength.

39:24.060 --> 39:28.190
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

39:27.350 --> 39:28.610
Then let's make a deal.

39:28.900 --> 39:30.460
I'll wait for you for a year and a half.

39:28.990 --> 39:31.900
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

39:31.130 --> 39:32.770
If you don't come back by then,

39:32.770 --> 39:34.540
I'll fly over and stick with you,

39:33.110 --> 39:35.170
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

39:34.650 --> 39:37.120
so you can't study or shake me off.

39:35.660 --> 39:37.390
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

39:47.810 --> 39:48.870
What should we do?

39:49.010 --> 39:50.610
I already started missing you.

39:49.210 --> 39:51.830
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

39:52.480 --> 39:53.960
Then we should

39:52.900 --> 39:54.900
♪ Don't look back ♪

39:53.960 --> 39:56.400
cherish the time we can spend together.

39:55.890 --> 39:57.730
♪ I've already learned ♪

39:56.550 --> 39:57.360
Yes.

39:57.920 --> 40:00.110
We should cherish each other's time more.

39:58.460 --> 40:02.260
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

40:02.980 --> 40:04.050
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

40:05.030 --> 40:09.860
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

40:10.390 --> 40:13.360
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

40:14.180 --> 40:16.510
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

40:15.590 --> 40:16.860
A year and a half.

40:17.220 --> 40:19.050
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

40:30.800 --> 40:32.210
I'll put the food here.

40:42.200 --> 40:43.200
Serving the food.

40:45.660 --> 40:46.660
Serving the food.

40:54.770 --> 40:55.290
Cheers.

40:55.780 --> 40:57.310
See you on the next journey.

40:58.080 --> 41:00.450
Our story ends here.

41:01.260 --> 41:03.100
Life continues.

41:03.510 --> 41:06.400
We may still argue,

41:06.430 --> 41:07.450
give each other the cold shoulder,

41:07.450 --> 41:08.570
or even break up.

41:09.100 --> 41:10.140
But

41:10.760 --> 41:12.640
as long as we still love each other,

41:12.640 --> 41:15.720
we will run to each other

41:16.040 --> 41:17.840
tirelessly over and over again.

41:27.700 --> 41:29.680
The world is chaotic and unpredictable.

41:29.680 --> 41:31.880
Life is inevitably a drifting journey.

41:32.400 --> 41:34.440
But we will eventually stop wandering

41:34.440 --> 41:35.810
for someone.

41:36.440 --> 41:40.230
We will eventually spread
our wings and fly for someone.
